Votes for Hillary Clinton and Donald Trump, 2016 Massachusetts Presidential Election

About

About this map

This map shows the number of votes received by Hillary Clinton and Donald Trump in the 2016 Massachusetts Presidential Election.

Each dot represents 100 votes. Click on a town for additional information.

Data is from the Massachusetts Secretary of the Commonwealth, mapped by Kent S Johnson.
